{"tid":435145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟學人：香港數碼安全全球60個城市排第5  鄰國上海排尾19","createTime":"2017-10-14T04:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T12:34:51.000Z","uid":136994,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"252dd4e573344e923974fde1b703664747ff0a31","tid":435145,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171014/57330166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171014%2F57330166&d=%2BSWCiBjWzNxvCbbo4lMCzePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=67cde88e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171014%2F57330166&h=40605818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171014/57330166</a><br />\n<br />\n據《經濟學人》2017年安全城市指數報告指，香港在全球60個受評分城市當中連升兩位打入十強，由2015年的第11位晉先至最新排第9。報告更指香港以「數碼安全」一項表現出色，排名全球第5。不少港人熱門外遊的亞洲城市都位於榜上頭20名，其中東京及新加坡分別霸佔榜首及第2名，而首爾亦排第14名。<br />\n<br />\n報告中指出，因2015年後本港警方設立「網絡安全及科技罪案調查科」，認為有助資訊科技鑑證並預防科技罪案，故於此範疇得分85.77，排全球第5。俄羅斯首都莫斯科則在此範疇評分中排名尾10（第51名），與越南胡志明市、菲律賓馬尼拉等國家的科技安全程度相約。<br />\n<br />\n榜上另一著眼點是早前遭恐襲的數個歐洲城市，如倫敦、巴黎等。《經濟學人》指，較高調而富裕的城市逐漸成為恐襲目標，這些城市或有較深層次的社會不公問題，今年倫敦排名較2015時下跌2位排20，巴黎則跌1位排名第24位；荷蘭阿姆斯特丹則成為最安全的歐洲城市，在全球排名第6。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/121044_b30cd5831b39ef92b174d0236ad75f25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F121044_b30cd5831b39ef92b174d0236ad75f25.png&h=36c7551f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/121057_ddc4a4c06183ad40c1f1ae620f469941.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F121057_ddc4a4c06183ad40c1f1ae620f469941.png&h=dd94aed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特衰政府唔係成日話香港數碼科技好落後嘅，要學習鄰國㗎嘛<br />\n咁鄰國喺「數碼安全」嘅排行榜入面去咗邊度呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b2984e3b135f03e2fc6d3c6635f76097969698","tid":435145,"uid":43845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:15:32.000Z","msg":"多得金管局"},{"pid":"0f2d127e8a4d43fb0d8072d09260d2e904a50386","tid":435145,"uid":43845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:15:32.000Z","msg":"多得金管局"},{"pid":"ebfa07e9b550b67e299fd5aece1012e3f93d8582","tid":435145,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"電話騙案算唔算科技罪案"},{"pid":"64de63bb50d21d063465b75f0c58e536f37894ad","tid":435145,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"中華台北呢？"},{"pid":"1b59b92b0a18acf90be2272a869a679b01a158f7","tid":435145,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054014ccb25762ed4fbdb832691e2496a93d847f","tid":435145,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中華台北呢？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/122136_cc97041266dd5efbdeb1194f1eecda23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F122136_cc97041266dd5efbdeb1194f1eecda23.png&h=ad39c333&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3b1f4550b50d8c3f35c568c0c97850b5294d9a5","tid":435145,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"哈！支那"},{"pid":"b6f70d1a8445a842f6e691c7eab90421d28f41f9","tid":435145,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"新加坡no. 2<img src=\"/assets/face